        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Marata's fiercest predators are also some of its most cunning hunters, leaving little sign when attempting to remain unseen. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to [[/act hide]] and [[/act sneak]] in natural terrain and a +1 circumstance bonus to Survival checks to @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.Cover Tracks] and [[/act track]] in natural terrain. You're always considered to be Covering Tracks, even if you chose a different activity in exploration mode.</p>"
